== About me
I am a research officer in [https://www.wehi.edu.au/people/gordon-smyth Prof. Gordon K Smyth] lab team at Bioinformatics Division, Walter and Eliza Hall Institute of Medical Research (WEHI). I completed my PhD degree in Statistics from the University of Melbourne under the supervision of [https://findanexpert.unimelb.edu.au/profile/144561-guoqi-qian A/Prof. Guoqi Qian], Prof. Yuriy Kuleshov and [https://findanexpert.unimelb.edu.au/profile/795463-tingjin-chu Dr. Tingjin Chu] in Jul. 2022. I received my M.S. and B.S. in Mathematics from Peking University on Jun. 2016 and Jul. 2013, respectively.

