== Softwares
- R package: edgeR (Empirical Analysis of Digital Gene Expression Data in R) \n
We develop the new quasi-likelihood method for differential expression analysis using the exact calculation for unit deviance of Negative Binomial distribution. It is available on [https://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/html/edgeR.html R-Bioconductor].
- R package: statmod (statmod: Statistical Modeling) \n 
We make the exact distributional calculations for unit deviances of Binomial, Poisson and Negative Binomial distributions. It is available on [https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/statmod/index.html R-CRAN].
- R package: IBGS (Iterated Blockwise Gibbs Sampler) \n
IBGS is an MCMC search algorithm designed to find the best model in the high dimensional data given a model selection criterion such as AIC, BIC and so on. Moreover, it can identify those most important covariates having the significant influence on the response. It is available on [https://github.com/lizhongc/IBGS Github].
